<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Backup Management - Marondera Court</title>
    <style>/* Same base styles */</style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">...</nav>
    <aside class="sidebar">...</aside>
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="page-header"><h1>Backup Management</h1></div>
        <div style="background:white; padding:2rem; border-radius:10px;">
            <h3 style="color:#1e3c72; margin-bottom:1rem;">Automated Backups</h3>
            <p>✅ Daily backups are automatically uploaded to AWS S3.</p>
            <p>📦 Total documents backed up: <strong><%= stats.totalDocuments %></strong></p>
            <p>💾 Total storage used: <strong><%= (stats.totalStorage / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> MB</strong></p>
            <p>🕒 Last backup: <strong><%= stats.lastBackup %></strong></p>
            <hr style="margin:1.5rem 0;">
            <p>Backups are stored in the <code>marondera-court-backups</code> S3 bucket.</p>
            <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn-primary">Back to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>